<doc id="1186937" wikidata="Q1640575" url="?curid=1186937" title="2004 MTV Europe Music Awards">
<text>The 2004 MTV Europe Music Awards were held at Tor di Valle Racecourse, Rome, Italy. As in 2003, the awards ceremony was held in a 6,000-capacity arena constructed specifically for the main event, called Valhalla Tensile 1, designed by Master Tentmaker Rudi Enos.

Award presenters on the night included Jamelia, Alicia Keys, N.E.R.D, Naomi Campbell, Andre 3000, Kid Rock and Kanye West.

