*&quot;The Garage&quot; (1980 film), a film by Eldar Ryazanov
=== Video game ===
*&quot;Garage&quot; (video game), a 1999 Japanese horror adventure video game

===Music===
====Groups and genres====
* Garage (band), a Czech rock band
* Garage house, a form of dance music that emerged in the 1980s
